snippet.title: Lifecraft Open Beta Steam Teaser
snippet.description:
Lifecraft is nearing the first step of its journey: Open Beta! 

Come join the beta on our Steam, download the beta for free and share your feedback in our Discord! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1839930/Lifecraft/

Have fun experimenting the endless possibilities of this fresh take on the base building games where life meets pixels!

Join our Discord if you want to share any feedback: https://discord.gg/TwsNSCHaN8
